title: Roll Away The Stone | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: Roll Away The Stone | Victoria Osteen
description:
Whatever you’re facing today, God has a promise prepared for you to overcome it! If you need strength or healing, remember His power in the Resurrection.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
